name: Dorje Legpa
shortLoreBlurb: Dorje Legpa is a deity/spirit from Tibet associated with thunder, protector. Tales link them to tempests and sky-sovereignty.
overlapsLinks: Athena (Greek), Indra (Vedic), Karttikeya (Hindu), Perun (Slavic), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Thor (Norse), Zeus (Greek)
